            "title": "全日收市︱跌幅擴大 恒指收挫331點報24035點 重磅科股領跌 創新藥股再揚",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中美貿易框架細節遲遲未公布，市場氣氛轉淡，港股午後跌幅擴大，以阿里巴巴(09988)等為首的重磅科股領跌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-ap_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-ap_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數今早低開143點後持續「潛水」，早市最多已曾跌逾200點，其後曾在內地A股倒升下稍為回順，午後沽壓卻再增加，指數跌破早市低位後不斷試底，一度逼近二萬四大關，低見24002點，挫364點；收報24035點，仍跌331點或1.36%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數明顯跑輸大市，收挫119點或2.2%，報5331點；國企指數跌135點或1.53%，報8729點。主板成交2444.12億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15004838-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e8%b7%8c%e5%b9%85%e6%93%b4%e5%a4%a7-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e6%8c%ab331%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b124035%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e7%a7%91%e8%82%a1%e9%a0%98",
